      <property name="text">
       <string>&lt;html&gt;&lt;head/&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;b&amp;gt;Create a strong password&amp;lt;/b&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Use at least 12 characters — longer passwords are more secure.&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Avoid common patterns like 123456 or qwerty.&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Don't use personal details like your name or birth date.&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A good strategy is to combine random words or create a memorable phrase.&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Try mixing uppercase letters, lowercase letters, numbers, and symbols.&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Avoid reusing passwords across different accounts.&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Keep your password private and change it if you think it's been exposed.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
